<p>ATMs (cash machines) provide essential financial services to individuals by provding access to cash, balance and account information and some other limited functions. The total number of ATMs in the UK peaked in 2015 and has fallen each year since then. <a href="https://www.link.co.uk/">Link</a> provide snapshots of the number of ATMs per Parliamentary constituency.</p>

