<h2>Notes</h2>
<p>Please note that where duplicate entries for a single machine are detected, then both current and historic data are adjusted, and this may mean that data does not precisely match previous reporting. Additionally, there may be very slight differences between the overall positions between the ‘Current’ and ‘Revised’ boundary reporting. This is due to the available data sources around the revised boundaries and LINK will align this information when the ONS publishes the required information for revised parliamentary constituency boundaries.</p>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       																					
																					
																					
